  "Description": "MODIFICATIONS:\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                DATASTAGE               CODE                           DATE\nDEVELOPER             DATE                PROJECT                     DESCRIPTION                                                                                      ENVIRONMENT          REVIEWER                 REVIEW\n-----------------------------    ----------------------     ------------------------------        -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  ------------------------------    ------------------------------       --------------------\n\nPooja Sunkara         2014-08-07              5345                             Original Programming                                                                         IntegrateWrhsDevl      Kalyan Neelam            2015-01-05\n\nAnnotations:\nJob Name: IdsProvLocLoad\nRead Load File created in the FKEY job\nCopy Stage for buffer\nUpdate then Insert PROV_LOC table\nLoad rejects are redirected into a Reject file"
